Invocation Name: story city church
des:
Listen to the latest messages from Story City Church in Burbank, California.

For the Story of God. For the City of LA. A community of grace and faith that considers your community its highest calling. Sundays at 10 & 11:30 AM. Learn more at www.storycitychurch.com.

You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done. You can also ask for previous and next messages by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next".
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
